  <name>Receiver</name>
  <summary>Internet radio player for GNOME</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      Receiver is a modern internet radio player for GNOME, featuring a curated collection of over 30,000 stations from around the world.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>All stations pre-scanned and verified for reliability</li>
      <li>Browse stations by genre, country, or search</li>
      <li>Save your favourite stations for quick access</li>
      <li>Beautiful native GNOME interface</li>
      <li>Support for MP3, AAC, Ogg, and HLS streams</li>
      <li>Session persistence - resume where you left off</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
